TITLE Benchmark 1: Linear Denitrification
SOLUTION 0
  temp 25
  pH 7.0
  pe 4
  units mg/L
  density 1
  N(5) 50
  Fe 1
  Cl 100
  Na 100
  -water 1 kg
END

SOLUTION 1-100 like 0
END

TRANSPORT
  cells 100
